### PERFORMANCE TEST 5: Large Data Retrieval

### Get all questions (test pagination performance)
GET {{baseUrl}}/cauhoi?page=1&pageSize=100
Authorization: Bearer {{teacherToken}}

### Get exam with all questions
GET {{baseUrl}}/exam/{{perfExamId}}/questions
Authorization: Bearer {{teacherToken}}

### Get session details with all answers
GET {{baseUrl}}/exam/{{perfSessionId}}/details
Authorization: Bearer {{teacherToken}}

### Get all anti-cheat logs
GET {{baseUrl}}/exam/{{perfSessionId}}/anticheat-logs
Authorization: Bearer {{teacherToken}}

### PERFORMANCE TEST 6: Complex Query Performance

### Search questions with filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/cauhoi/search?keyword=performance&mucDo=3&idDanhMuc=1
Authorization: Bearer {{teacherToken}}

### Get exam statistics (complex aggregation)
GET {{baseUrl}}/exam/{{perfExamId}}/statistics
Authorization: Bearer {{teacherToken}}

### Get comprehensive results
GET {{baseUrl}}/exam/{{perfExamId}}/results
Authorization: Bearer {{teacherToken}}

